  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Messticulous</strong>, <strong>aim and</strong> <strong>throw objects to unusual spots</strong> following a completely wacky 'tidy up' system, all with <strong>physics-based gameplay</strong> that reminds mini-golf games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accomplish wacky tidying challenges in the least practical way </strong>that will push the limits of your ingenuity and precision, so that, in the end, everything still looks pretty messy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meticulously prepare your throws, find the right trajectories, exploit bounces and avoid obstacles to send each object where it \"belongs\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/72b1dbabc92164505fe6aa8e9c4dc158.poster.avif?t=1732832234\" width=720 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/72b1dbabc92164505fe6aa8e9c4dc158.webm?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/72b1dbabc92164505fe6aa8e9c4dc158.mp4?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1732832234\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unusual way of tidying up that's 100% original!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaotic, zany gameplay based entirely on physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of challenging trick shots to complete in 19 rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+90 minutes of playtime</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And, for the last time, yes, this is where it goes. I have my own system... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, the slipper goes in the bowl. Why do you ask?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A word from the development team </strong>(even though there's only one person):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hi, I'm Ludovic, the game developer. I just wanted to tell you that I created Messticulous because I really like offbeat games and physics-based challenges! I hope you're going to have a great time throwing all these objects to wacky places to 'tidy up'!</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Messticulous</strong>, <strong>aim and</strong> <strong>throw objects to unusual spots</strong> following a completely wacky 'tidy up' system, all with <strong>physics-based gameplay</strong> that reminds mini-golf games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accomplish wacky tidying challenges in the least practical way </strong>that will push the limits of your ingenuity and precision, so that, in the end, everything still looks pretty messy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meticulously prepare your throws, find the right trajectories, exploit bounces and avoid obstacles to send each object where it \"belongs\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/72b1dbabc92164505fe6aa8e9c4dc158.poster.avif?t=1732832234\" width=720 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/72b1dbabc92164505fe6aa8e9c4dc158.webm?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/72b1dbabc92164505fe6aa8e9c4dc158.mp4?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1732832234\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1301880/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1732832234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unusual way of tidying up that's 100% original!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaotic, zany gameplay based entirely on physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of challenging trick shots to complete in 19 rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+90 minutes of playtime</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And, for the last time, yes, this is where it goes. I have my own system... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, the slipper goes in the bowl. Why do you ask?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A word from the development team </strong>(even though there's only one person):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hi, I'm Ludovic, the game developer. I just wanted to tell you that I created Messticulous because I really like offbeat games and physics-based challenges! I hope you're going to have a great time throwing all these objects to wacky places to 'tidy up'!</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
